reviews.text: Decently priced ramen. The pork belly was too chewy and not soft or tender. Another drawback here is that the air conditioning is weak. So I was still sweating inside on a hot day.
Small and noisy place. Be aware you'll have to share the table. The food is very tasty though.
Delicious ramen. Pork belly skewers are very tasty too. All with a bottle of sake and you're good to go!
I tried the spicy ramen. & Ouu Delicious!
Nice place. The Black ramen is very nice
